  "title": "Ais-Rating-Menu ssr problems.",
  "body": "**Bug 🐞**\r\n\r\n### What is the current behavior?\r\nAis-Rating-Menu not working as expected. \r\n\r\nSeveral observations:\r\nMenu not selectable/links not working.\r\nSeems to get out of sync due to SSR.\r\n\r\nEnter via root. Navigate to search. Rating works as expected.\r\nRefresh page. Rating no longer works. \r\nAlso, if you navigate to the search page via url in browser (localhost:3000/search) Rating doesn't work.\r\n\r\n### Make a sandbox with the current behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/jaylingelbach/uvue-sandbox\r\n\r\n### What is the expected behavior?\r\nRating always works no matter how you get there.\r\n\r\n### Does this happen only in specific situations?\r\n\r\nYes. Via url navigation or refresh.\r\n\r\n### What is the proposed solution?\r\n\r\nInvestigate ssr with rating menu in Vue.\r\n\r\n### What is the version you are using?\r\nlatest\r\n> Always try the latest one before opening an issue.\r\n",
